overview.en: UEBT is a platform for Ultra-election over-selection based on blockchain and smart contract technology to incubate the sharing economy and generate quantitative value for users' network behavior and idle resources.
overview.zh: UEBT 是 Ultra-election 超选基于区块链及智能合约技术，孵化共享经济，让用户网络行为及闲置资源产生量化价值的平台通证。
